NSL Renewable May Raise $80 Million From Private Equity Funds to Expand

-- B y   S h a r a n g   L i m a y e
-- 
2011-05-05T05:29:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-05/nsl-renewable-may-raise-80-million-from-private-equity-funds-to-expand.html
NSL Renewable Power Pvt. is in talks
with private equity funds to raise as much as $80 million from
sale of shares to add capacity, N.M. Vaidyanathan, chief
financial officer of NSL Group, said in a telephone interview
from Hyderabad yesterday.  The money will be raised within 60 days and used for
setting up hydroelectric generation plants and wind power
projects, Vaidyanathan said. The International Finance Corp.
yesterday agreed to invest $20 million in the Hyderabad-based
company, he said.    To contact the reporter on this story:
Sharang Limaye in Hyderabad at 
